    "attributes": {
        "action": "Legalise tandem mobility scooters in the UK",
        "additional_details": "Current laws prevent them from doing so \u2013 and yet the Government does not have any plans to amend the legislation to make them lawful.\r\n\r\nWe\u2019d like to help get the law changed if you can please sign our petition.",
        "background": "It seems obvious why tandem mobility scooters can be so useful for older couples \u2013 especially when one person is no longer able to operate a scooter on their own or disabled mobility scooter owners  who may need to transport  their child to school.",
